properties.name: Plenty, Swalecliffe and West Brooks
properties.river_sea: Plenty Brook, Swalecliffe Brook, West Brook
properties.description: Plenty Brook from Eddington to the sea, including Herne Bay, the Swalecliffe Brook from near Court Lees to the sea, including Chestfield and Swalecliffe and the West Brook from the railway line to the sea including Studd Hill and Hampton
